<dim:field qualifier="abstract" mdschema="dc" language="en_US" element="description">This seven-minute piece transcends boundaries for gender and character, while charting a man's struggle to embody his own metamorphosis. Sparling's solo reveals four physical personalities each of which mirrors the voices in Arvo Part's score.  Peter Sparling: performer and editor; Jacques Mersereau: videographer; and Tom Bray: video finishing.</dim:field>
